<h4 class="artikel">Who we are</h4>
<h1>European Union General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) (valid May 25, 2018)</h1>
<p class="intro">The protection of your personal data is very important to us at Deutsche Welle. We want you to feel safe when using our websites. We explain here what data we collect and how we use it.</p>
<div id="sharing-bar" class="min">
